gurmukhi: AwnMd srUpI Anhd rUpI Acl ibBUqI Bv qrxM ]
translation: Thou art Blissful and Unlimited Entity, of stable wealth and the causer of swimming across the dreadful world-ocean.

gurmukhi: AngwiD AbwDM jgq pRswDM srb ArwDM qv srxM ]3]23]
transliteration: Anaddh(i) Abaadhan Jagad Prasaadhan Sarab Araadhan Tav Saranan||3||23||
translation: Thou art the unfathomable, Unattached, Keeper of the world under discipline and meditated upon by all; I am in Thy refuge.3.23.

gurmukhi: AklMk AbwD ibsu pRswDM jgq ArwDM Bv nwsM ]
transliteration: Akalank Abaadhan Bis(u) Prasaadhan Jagad Araadhan Bhav Naasan||
translation: Thou art Unblemished, Unattached, Keeper of the Universe under discipline, remembered by the world and destroyer of fear.

gurmukhi: ibsÍMBr BrxM iklivK hrxM piqq auDrxM sB swQM ]
transliteration: Bisvanbhar Bharanan Kilvikh Haranan Patit Udharanan Sabh Saathan||
translation: Thou art the Sustainer of the universe, destroyer of sins, redeemer of the sinners and be comrade of all.

gurmukhi: AnwQn nwQy AkiRq AgwQy Aimq AnwQy duK hrxM ]
transliteration: Anaathan Naathe Akrit Agaddhe Amit Anaathe Doukh Haranan||
translation: Thou art the Master of the masterless, Uncreated, Undescribed, Unlimited, Patronless and remover of sufferings.

gurmukhi: AgMj AibnwsI jyiq pRkwsI jgq pRxwsI quX srxM ]4]24]
translation: Thou art Invincible, Indestructible, Illuminator of Light, the destroyer of the world, I am in Thy refuge.4.24.

gurmukhi: Aimq qyj jg joiq pRkwsI ]Awid ACyd ABY AibnwsI ]
transliteration: Amit Tej Jag Jot Parakaasee|| Aadh Ached Abhai Abinaasee||
translation: Thou art of Unlimited brilliance and Thy Light hath illumined the world; thou art Primal, Unassailable, Fearless and Indestructible.

gurmukhi: prm q`q prmwrQ pRkwsI ]Awid srUp AKMf audwsI ]5]25]
transliteration: Param Tatt Parmaarath Prakaansee|| Aadh Saroopakhannddudaasee||5||25||
translation: Thou art the Supreme Essence and enlightener of the path of subtle Truth; Thou art Primal entity, Indivisible and Unattached.5.25.

gurmukhi: AKMf audwsI prm pRkwsI Awid AnwsI ibsÍ krM ]
translation: Thou art Indivisible, Unattached, the Supreme Enlightener, Primal, Indestructible and Creator of the universe.

gurmukhi: jgqwvl krqw jgq pHrqw sB jg Brqw is`D BrM ]
transliteration: Jagadaaval Kartaa Jagad Prahartaa Sabh Jag Bhartaa Siddh Bharan||
translation: Thou art the creator, destroyer and Sustainer of the world and the Treasure of Powers.

gurmukhi: ACY AibnwsI qyj pRkwsI rUp surwsI srb iCqM ]
translation: Thou art Unassailable, Indestructible, Illuminator of the Light, and the outlay of beauty of all the earth.

gurmukhi: AwnMd srUpI Anhd rUpI AlK ibBUqI Aimq gqM ]6]26]
translation: Thou art Blissful and Unlimited Entity, Incomprehensible wealth and of Unlimited movement.6.26.
